{"tid":4502,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［宵夜］出前一丁 香辣麻油味","createTime":"2016-11-26T13:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T02:08:44.000Z","uid":3066,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9956d5332a22fce9ab01602f89cf3c0f950efb55","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"琴晚整完雞蓉味 無餸 其實我唔鐘意個味 所以麻麻地 比左4.5/10分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日有巴打教左整流心蛋 今日試左感覺上唔係好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日就試香辣麻油味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/215217_76c770d24292dd2222cd4b8be6550aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F215217_76c770d24292dd2222cd4b8be6550aca.jpg&h=1af2e34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n配料有少少蔥同兩條腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然唔少得失敗左既流心蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MN1T91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMN1T91.jpg&h=daa6a965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲品方面當然係健康既水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rn6wD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rn6wD.jpg&h=7d7c7e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個流心蛋打落去係橙黃色 做唔到鮮黃既效果<br />\n算唔算成功？ 我覺得好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/215649_06d107b0629c502b99b677848329eedf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F215649_06d107b0629c502b99b677848329eedf.jpg&h=234ca4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/215649_1bfe1020c8b157a3f4d8627660829e4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F215649_1bfe1020c8b157a3f4d8627660829e4e.jpg&h=b50e4c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整體黎講比6.8/10分 不能再高<br />\n麻油味好正 不過都唔算太辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個湯飲落去都ok<br />\n<br />\n最後送上蛋殻圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ez0p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ez0p3.jpg&h=53ac42e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76e9aedf9fbb7b841b4cdf7493e8c63557ce3a25","tid":4502,"uid":22671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"浪費曬d 蛋汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddb0867526fc51915a1d9de5ce15f5178b13e77","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浪費曬d 蛋汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少少啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f8d1d570dfbe2ba515bc26eb498bb9c6c39111","tid":4502,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"睇見最尾幅圖 碌鳩唔知點解莫名奇妙地痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40810af357d1ef694c60a3cc192dc61c2a282f6e","tid":4502,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f87bb58e782dc46fd1d44e3f863d93a552b115f","tid":4502,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"廢青狗糧"},{"pid":"4a02b7ef515787b04c6338357ef9057e06e7d3b5","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢青狗糧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次整埋比你食 岩你"},{"pid":"68403602f271fe2425d5457146de69f08c6a0402","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊忽流心？生蛋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以話失敗左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374b37cec2c9bbd104170b5002ca0232bb8e3d00","tid":4502,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"濃湯先好食"},{"pid":"553baafac262e775b8b9f681f72c670d79758a65","tid":4502,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肚餓呀"},{"pid":"b1c0353cd71343faabc51bd60dccd1f40dd49933","tid":4502,"uid":9989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"張蛋殼圖做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ee3a245fb2a552d31bbf6b27ef341edf182e5e","tid":4502,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"樓主煮腸仔嗰陣係擺埋落個麵度一齊煮？"},{"pid":"0ac1709fcfd1df0e75b48d2c770e2def24a85801","tid":4502,"uid":10689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"腸仔唔煎<br />\n失敗"},{"pid":"c75467bb15fdd567148f1082778a2a5f69ebbbb9","tid":4502,"uid":72,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T19:38:27.000Z","msg":"幾時開餐廳"},{"pid":"ff25b407fa91d137e96408ec9c13aa890021a498","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主煮腸仔嗰陣係擺埋落個麵度一齊煮？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係"},{"pid":"1b2b91dcd03c0c47598a0251b7f151dc534de3da","tid":4502,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時開餐廳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪可以好似一蘭咁呃到女女黎打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152a42b36cbd4b86de62fcc84e